{"content": "I need to multiply 833\u2089 \u00d7 283\u2089.\n\n**Step 1: Convert to base 10**\n\n833\u2089 = 8\u00d79\u00b2 + 3\u00d79\u00b9 + 3\u00d79\u2070 = 8\u00d781 + 3\u00d79 + 3\u00d71 = 648 + 27 + 3 = 678\u2081\u2080\n\n283\u2089 = 2\u00d79\u00b2 + 8\u00d79\u00b9 + 3\u00d79\u2070 = 2\u00d781 + 8\u00d79 + 3\u00d71 = 162 + 72 + 3 = 237\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 2: Multiply in base 10**\n\n678 \u00d7 237 = 160,686\u2081\u2080\n\n**Step 3: Convert result to base 9**\n\n160686 \u00f7 9 = 17854 r 0\n17854 \u00f7 9 = 1983 r 7\n1983 \u00f7 9 = 220 r 3\n220 \u00f7 9 = 24 r 4\n24 \u00f7 9 = 2 r 6\n2 \u00f7 9 = 0 r 2\n\nReading from bottom to top: **264370\u2089**\n\n264370", "model": "anthropic/claude-sonnet-4.5", "prompt_tokens": 1150, "completion_tokens": 325}